{"tid":337403,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【股神也要聽】華爾街大師：比特幣似「騙局」 (16:36)","createTime":"2017-07-27T09:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T03:57:33.000Z","uid":17738,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"189684857c01331266fdc6fc43d78e90bdef7cc2","tid":337403,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170727/img/20170727163654fi_p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170727%2Fimg%2F20170727163654fi_p1.jpg&h=68cb30cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=jJesrG7db7hc%2F08bn%2FGEQDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=4a861305\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】外國傳媒報道，華爾街最受尊敬的意見領袖之一、連「股神」巴菲特也是其「粉絲」的投資大師橡樹資本(Oaktree Capital)董事長及聯合創辦人馬克斯(Howard Marks)，最新向客戶發信件警告，不要盲目跟風買以比特幣為首的虛擬貨幣，這種資產的價格高得離譜。<br />\n<br />\n71歲的馬克斯表示，在他的角度來看來，虛擬貨幣只是流行一時的玩意，或者甚至就是一種類似龐氏騙局的「金字塔騙局」，只是將價值歸於某種東西，這種東西除了人們願意支付的價格外，幾乎毫無價值。<br />\n<br />\n馬克斯將虛擬貨幣與1637年的荷蘭郁金香狂熱、1720年的南海泡沫，以及1999年的科網泡沫進行比較，嚴正指出虛擬貨幣是投機多於投資，投資者已不考慮其內在價值或價格。<br />\n<br />\n馬克斯曾準確預測2001年科網爆泡及2008年金融海嘯。巴菲特曾說：「當我一看見馬克斯給我的信件，我一定是立即打開及閱讀。」可想而知馬克斯的地位之高。<br />\n<br />\n今年截至本周三(7月26日)為止，「龍頭」比特幣已累漲近1.6倍；「二哥」以太幣更狂飆23倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170727/20170727163654fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170727%2F20170727163654fi.html&d=jJesrG7db7hc%2F08bn%2FGEQDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=d7c3013b\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170727/20170727163654fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"1769fc2f1258f991eba57aa598deed10e120ed25","tid":337403,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:16:49.000Z","msg":"本來就係黑市用 係d大陸人炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c8d963d606877b8aab8c17b59289ff12725048","tid":337403,"uid":128660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:29:55.000Z","msg":"比特幣其實都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab2ab0c21b1eafb9181e34d951ded1e3be8b5d00","tid":337403,"uid":56607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T03:57:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}